#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.89"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.89:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.89:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga "
msgstr "9. Ascetics "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.89:0.3"
msgid "89. Paṭhamasikkhattayasutta "
msgstr "89. Three Trainings (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.89:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, sikkhā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these are the three trainings. "

msgctxt "an3.89:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.89:1.3"
msgid "Adhisīlasikkhā, adhicittasikkhā, adhipaññāsikkhā. "
msgstr "The training in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.89:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, adhisīlasikkhā? "
msgstr "And what is the training in the higher ethics? "

msgctxt "an3.89:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is ethical, restrained in the code of conduct, with good behavior and supporters. Seeing danger in the slightest fault, they keep the rules they’ve undertaken. "

msgctxt "an3.89:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, adhisīlasikkhā. "
msgstr "This is called the training in the higher ethics. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.89:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, adhicittasikkhā? "
msgstr "And what is the training in the higher mind? "

msgctxt "an3.89:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first absorption … second absorption … third absorption … fourth absorption. "

msgctxt "an3.89:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, adhicittasikkhā. "
msgstr "This is called the training in the higher mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an3.89:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, adhipaññāsikkhā? "
msgstr "And what is the training in the higher wisdom? "

msgctxt "an3.89:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "They truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

msgctxt "an3.89:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, adhipaññāsikkhā. "
msgstr "This is called the training in the higher wisdom. "

msgctxt "an3.89:4.4"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso sikkhā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three trainings.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.89:4.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

